was called a sliced almond.

00:02:45.640 --> 00:02:48.460
I used to think that they were slivered almonds.

00:02:48.460 --> 00:02:50.860
So, always room to learn.

00:02:50.860 --> 00:02:57.220
The second thing is, stewing the fruit, which
has been diced here finely.

00:02:57.220 --> 00:03:03.590
The purpose here of dicing them finely is
so that specifically for small servings like

00:03:03.590 --> 00:03:06.690
