00:03:51.740 --> 00:03:56.880
But some prefer, and again that's a question
of preference, some people prefer when it's

00:03:56.880 --> 00:03:57.880
cold.

00:03:57.880 --> 00:03:59.710
Some people keep that in the fridge.

00:03:59.710 --> 00:04:02.190
I, myself, like that when it's lukewarm.

00:04:02.190 --> 00:04:05.120
So, you just choose again what's best for
you.

00:04:05.120 --> 00:04:11.730
