00:24:34.710 --> 00:24:35.710
You know, at other people's house, or in a
restaurant.

00:24:35.710 --> 00:24:36.710
So it's a combination of those things and
like I said, I think travel is a big one.

00:24:36.710 --> 00:24:37.710
Because it just gives me a different perspective
and understanding and trying to be creative

00:24:37.710 --> 00:24:38.710
again.

